      303.36
    ],
    "text": "site, was abducted by unidentified individuals on 02nd of February 2012. This incident was",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      310.84,
      526.44,
      324.12
    ],
    "text": "witnessed by a local resident, Mohammed Hussain. During the abduction, a magazine",
