      "Times New Roman",
      "Times New Roman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      331.48,
      526.02,
      344.76
    ],
    "text": "cartridge was dropped by the abductors and subsequently handed over to the Police. The",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      352.24,
      526.0,
      365.52
    ],
    "text": "family of the corpus promptly lodged a complaint with the Wellampitiya Police Station.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      372.88,
      526.42,
      386.16
    ],
    "text": "Despite this complaint, no information about the corpuss whereabouts was obtained.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      393.52,
      526.07,
      406.8
    ],
    "text": "Consequently, the Petitioner and his family sought assistance from various organizations to",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      414.3,
      526.1,
      427.58
    ],
    "text": "locate the corpus. The Petitioner asserts that, notwithstanding these efforts, he received no",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      434.94,
      526.32,
      448.22
    ],
    "text": "information regarding the whereabouts of the corpus, and the Police were unable to trace him.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      474.83,
      526.12,
      490.1
    ],
