    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      538.98,
      526.09,
      552.26
    ],
    "text": "individuals as being present during the corpuss abduction. The Petitioner promptly reported",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      559.62,
      525.98,
      572.9
    ],
    "text": "this identification to the Wellampitiya Police. The Petitioner was informed by the Police that",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      580.41,
      526.18,
      593.69
    ],
    "text": "the apprehended individuals were members of the Sri Lanka Army and would be produced in",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      601.05,
      526.21,
      614.33
    ],
    "text": "court. According to the aforementioned reasons the Petitioner alleges that the corpus is being",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      621.81,
      287.35,
      635.09
    ],
    "text": "unlawfully detained by the Sri Lanka Army.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      659.9,
      526.19,
      675.17
    ],
    "text": "However, on 11th of March 2012, the Petitioner was informed by the Police that the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      682.65,
      526.14,
      695.93
    ],
    "text": "apprehended individuals had been released to the custody of the Sri Lanka Army and had not",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      703.29,
      526.1,
      716.57
    ],
    "text": "been presented before the Court. The Petitioner contends that no proper investigation has",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      724.07,
      526.38,
      737.35
    ],
    "text": "been conducted regarding the whereabouts of the corpus. Furthermore, there is no evidence",
    "fonts": [
